{"word":"G2221 - ζωγρέω - zōgréō - dzogue-reh'-o - Take captive","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ζωγρέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">zōgréō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dzogue-reh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Take captive</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பிடி, பிடிக்கிறவனாயிரு"},{"paragraph":"1. to take alive"},{"paragraph":"2. to take, catch, capture"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From the same as <a href=\"#/G2226 - ζῶον - zōon - dzo'-on/2226\">G2226</a> and <a href=\"#/G64 - ἀγρεύω - agreúō - ag-rew'-o/64\">G64</a>; to <i>take alive</i> (<i>make a prisoner of war</i>), that is, (figuratively) to <i>capture</i> or <i>ensnare:</i> - take captive, catch.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}